                            Dr. Veritas's Personnel File
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/the-great-hippo/scp_trans.png) center no-repeat ; float: center; border: solid 2px #000000; padding: 1px 15px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>Personnel Record Access</span></h1>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc1"><span>Note that access to personnel files is restricted to clearance level 3.</span></h3>
</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-0f2c6c2ac763174f17a652c2c48113c1" class="yui-navset">
